title: Command & Conquer 3 Kane's Wrath-install.zip
description:
Command & Conquer 3 Kane's Wrath

Instructions:

1 - UnZip the file, you'll get the folder "Command & Conquer 3 Kane's Wrath-install".
2 - Copy the folder inside your "Program Files" folder and rename, remove the -install at the end.
3 - Run as administrator "setup.bat".
4 - This will install and create shotcuts (keep original zip or folder for future installs).

Enjoy

This version let's you update like the original.
